    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_1076024201250877667.png",
                "id": "talent74824",
                "key": "水有常形",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水有常形"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素戰技</span></p><p>本角色<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">附著水元素</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">化海月</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/b33ca2371d6c02d581a1a89570bc6fb8_5474092769544138088.png",
                "id": "talent64491",
                "key": "海月之誓",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "海月之誓"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素傷害</span>，治療所有我方角色1點，本角色附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">儀來羽衣</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">儀來羽衣</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p>所附屬角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">普通攻擊</span>造成的傷害+1。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附屬角色普通攻擊後：</span>治療所有我方角色1點。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持續回合：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/47fcf95dc439392467286728a046b049_2883741230524453039.png",
                "id": "talent11136",
                "key": "海人化羽",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "海人化羽"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素傷害</span>，治療我方出戰角色1點。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1401284748026778801.png",
                "id": "talent18189",
                "key": "化海月",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/0e046eb8f7da357cc6b2ee42e058526a_8144329499546270603.png",
                "title": "化海月"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>不透過傷害<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">附著水元素</span>時，發生的元素反應會忽略傷害效果：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：沒有效果</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：沒有效果</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害后提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：生成使下次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「草原核」</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_7137525793140700163.png",
                "id": "talent34858",
                "key": "附著水元素",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "附著水元素"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感電</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害后提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">綻放</span>：本傷害+1，生成使下次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>傷害+2的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「草原核」</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出戰狀態</span></p><p>我方對敵方出戰角色造成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素傷害</span>時，傷害值+2。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_2710166681067496482.png",
                "id": "talent84248",
                "key": "水元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">持續回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合結束階段，持續回合-1；</p><p>持續回合耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_7754128901057808360.png",
